<div class="post">
<div class="inner" id="msg_1125305">官方主页7月10号发文表示Legends of Barsaive（以下简称LoB）将迎来第九个冒险<strong>Once Bitten, Twiceborn</strong>。在本贴撰写的21号该冒险已经上架有几天了，<a href="https://www.drivethrurpg.com/product/364002/Legends-of-Barsaive-09-Once-Bitten-Twiceborn" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">D站购买地址</a>，此外在FASA的主页线上商店也可以购买。<br><br><div align="center"><a href="https://imgtu.com/i/Ww9Lxe" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank"><img src="https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/07/21/Ww9Lxe.png" alt="" class="bbc_img"/></a></div><br>LoB的冒险目前主要围绕着曾经是帝国的省首府的帕尔莱因斯展开，在这座城市回到巴尔塞夫之后被巨魔托尔加克控制的部分被称为避风港。前1-8本书（实际上是小册子）已经整合修订成了一本书，<a href="https://www.drivethrurpg.com/product/351922/Legends-of-Barsaive-Haven-Volume-1" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">D站购买地址</a>。<br><br>以下分别简要介绍这些册子的内容，内含剧透：<br><br><strong>LoB100-Masks of Fear：</strong><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">一个小序章，快速入门包的一部分，可以在商店免费获得。冒险主要围绕着一些系统的机制（特别是对抗生物、惧魔构装体和习艺者的战斗）展开，也介绍了些战役里重要的GM角色。</div></div></div><br><strong>LoB101-Toys in the Attic：</strong><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">提供了社交方面的一些东西，避风港周围城镇的信息可以成为战役种子。</div></div></div><br><strong>LoB102-Lip Service、LoB103-Separation Anxiety：</strong><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">避风港的街头政治和派系争端，包括托尔加克、非所属探索者协会（AUE）、索洛尔、锡拉以及血林在避风港的势力冲突。</div></div></div><br><strong>LoB104-That Which Was Lost：</strong><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">延续LoB101的故事，同时引入了名为火棘靴（Firethorn Boots）的脉路物品。</div></div></div><br><strong>LoB105-Games of the Hungry：</strong><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">这个冒险更独立，主要着眼于帕尔莱因斯废墟中的战争游戏。在这座城市沦陷之后，潜入城中的惧魔尽享折磨居民的乐趣，接着发觉自己被困在了帕尔莱因斯城中。于是它们在这段被囚禁的时间里操纵腐化的伪人等构装体在城市中进行着无尽的战争游戏，用这些傀儡当作棋子去攻陷彼此的领地、抢掠被当成筹码的逝者的财富。和LoB104一样，本冒险也引入了新的脉路物品。</div></div></div><br><strong>LoB106-Glass Houses：</strong><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.pa